Dialogue: 10,0:00:03.14,0:00:05.81,GJM_Main,,0,0,0,,I'm... going to die?
Dialogue: 10,0:00:05.81,0:00:10.07,GJM_Main,,0,0,0,,The Oracle cells have acclimated\Nto your body and will continue to spread,
Dialogue: 10,0:00:10.07,0:00:12.40,GJM_Main,,0,0,0,,eventually consuming you.
Dialogue: 10,0:00:12.40,0:00:15.20,GJM_Main,,0,0,0,,If you continue to use your God Arc,{ep8 preview line}
Dialogue: 10,0:00:15.20,0:00:19.33,GJM_Main,,0,0,0,,I have no doubt that your\Ncompatibility rate will accelerate.
Dialogue: 10,0:00:21.54,0:00:24.79,GJM_Main,,0,0,0,,What if I stopped using my God Arc?
Dialogue: 10,0:00:25.29,0:00:27.67,GJM_Main,,0,0,0,,Then I'd give you another\Nthree years to live at most.
Dialogue: 10,0:00:29.38,0:00:33.13,GJM_Main,,0,0,0,,I'm sorry, but you can't stave off the inevitable.
Dialogue: 10,0:00:33.46,0:00:37.93,GJM_Main,,0,0,0,,My advice is to retire as a God Eater\Nto give yourself more time.
Dialogue: 10,0:00:37.93,0:00:41.72,GJM_Main,,0,0,0,,Though, even if you do,\Nwe'll have to continue regulating your Bias Factor.
Dialogue: 10,0:00:41.72,0:00:43.23,GJM_Main,,0,0,0,,My Bias Factor?
Dialogue: 10,0:00:43.68,0:00:48.77,GJM_Main,,0,0,0,,Like any Aragami, the Oracle cells\Nin your body have a bias inclination.
Dialogue: 10,0:00:49.27,0:00:54.32,GJM_Main,,0,0,0,,If left unchecked,\Nthey'll run rampant, and you will die.
Dialogue: 10,0:00:54.82,0:00:58.66,GJM_Main,,0,0,0,,Since you've become a God Eater,\Nyou can no longer leave Fenrir.
Dialogue: 10,0:00:59.32,0:01:02.87,GJM_Main,,0,0,0,,If you still want to fight knowing this, however...
Dialogue: 10,0:01:04.33,0:01:06.17,GJM_Main,,0,0,0,,I will restore your God Arc.
Dialogue: 10,0:01:07.21,0:01:08.54,GJM_Main,,0,0,0,,It's your call.
Dialogue: 10,0:01:09.79,0:01:11.17,GJM_Main,,0,0,0,,Who else knows about this?
Dialogue: 10,0:01:12.05,0:01:14.05,GJM_Main,,0,0,0,,Only Licca and myself.
Dialogue: 10,0:01:14.80,0:01:16.43,GJM_Main,,0,0,0,,I want you to think about it.
Dialogue: 10,0:01:21.18,0:01:23.39,GJM_Main,,0,0,0,,{\i1}This is a huge step forward for mankind.
Dialogue: 10,0:01:23.89,0:01:27.52,GJM_Main,,0,0,0,,{\i1}There's no sign of rejection at all.\NHis compatibility rate is stunning.
Dialogue: 10,0:01:28.02,0:01:31.02,GJM_Main,,0,0,0,,{\i1}A hybrid of man and Aragami...
Dialogue: 10,0:01:31.02,0:01:33.32,GJM_Main,,0,0,0,,{\i1}By analyzing this child's compatibility...
Dialogue: 10,0:01:33.82,0:01:37.24,GJM_Main,,0,0,0,,{\i1}we'll be able to engineer humans\Nthat can stand up to the Aragami.
Dialogue: 10,0:01:37.24,0:01:38.82,GJM_Main,,0,0,0,,{\i1}A God Eater, you might say...
Dialogue: 10,0:01:39.36,0:01:41.28,GJM_Main,,0,0,0,,{\i1}Look at this reaction!
Dialogue: 10,0:01:43.95,0:01:45.66,GJM_Main,,0,0,0,,Wh-What a monster...
Dialogue: 10,0:01:58.05,0:01:59.34,GJM_Main,,0,0,0,,Damn it...
Dialogue: 10,0:02:06.60,0:02:08.48,GJM_Main,,0,0,0,,There's a rat in the bedroom.
Dialogue: 10,0:02:09.31,0:02:11.94,GJM_Main,,0,0,0,,Send for a cat.
Dialogue: 10,0:02:15.75,0:02:18.84,GJM_Main,,0,0,0,,The giant protrusions around the world,
Dialogue: 10,0:02:18.84,0:02:21.96,GJM_Main,,0,0,0,,which were causing damage on a global scale,
Dialogue: 10,0:02:21.96,0:02:25.79,GJM_Main,,0,0,0,,have stopped as mysteriously as they began.
Dialogue: 10,0:02:26.18,0:02:29.50,GJM_Main,,0,0,0,,The U.N. is directing all available resources\Ntowards rescue and reconstruction.
Dialogue: 10,0:02:29.50,0:02:33.10,GJM_Main,,0,0,0,,However, the unknown lifeforms\Nthat have appeared since,
Dialogue: 10,0:02:33.10,0:02:38.19,GJM_Main,,0,0,0,,dubbed "the menace of the gods" or "Aragami",
Dialogue: 10,0:02:38.19,0:02:41.93,GJM_Main,,0,0,0,,have proven impervious to every weapon\Nused against them, and casualties are—
Dialogue: 10,0:02:46.49,0:02:50.58,GJM_Main,,0,0,0,,If we had reported this sooner...
Dialogue: 10,0:02:51.70,0:02:53.00,GJM_Main,,0,0,0,,Johannes...
Dialogue: 10,0:02:53.00,0:02:56.75,GJM_Main,,0,0,0,,You're right. Maybe we could have\Nreduced the number of casualties.
Dialogue: 10,0:02:56.75,0:02:57.88,GJM_Main,,0,0,0,,Paylor!
Dialogue: 10,0:02:57.88,0:02:59.75,GJM_Main,,0,0,0,,Don't you think it's strange?
Dialogue: 10,0:03:01.11,0:03:05.26,GJM_Main,,0,0,0,,Amidst the darkness,\Nonly those marks emit light.
Dialogue: 10,0:03:10.10,0:03:11.58,GJM_Main,,0,0,0,,That light...
Dialogue: 10,0:03:13.33,0:03:17.14,GJM_Main,,0,0,0,,You don't think the higher-ups\Nused that technology...
Dialogue: 10,0:03:17.14,0:03:20.36,GJM_Main,,0,0,0,,Let's call it the Bias Factor.
Dialogue: 10,0:03:20.36,0:03:23.90,GJM_Main,,0,0,0,,Those protrusions sure are picky eaters.
Dialogue: 10,0:03:23.90,0:03:26.18,GJM_Main,,0,0,0,,Does that mean Fenrir\Nanticipated this happening?
Dialogue: 10,0:03:26.65,0:03:27.91,GJM_Main,,0,0,0,,It makes you wonder.
Dialogue: 10,0:03:31.16,0:03:32.16,GJM_Main,,0,0,0,,Paylor...
Dialogue: 10,0:03:33.33,0:03:36.91,GJM_Main,,0,0,0,,Do you think the Bias Factor\Ncan be weaponized?
Dialogue: 10,0:03:36.91,0:03:39.33,GJM_Main,,0,0,0,,It's hard to say for sure\Nwithout running more tests.
Dialogue: 10,0:03:39.33,0:03:40.29,GJM_Main,,0,0,0,,Johannes?
Dialogue: 10,0:03:41.13,0:03:45.16,GJM_Main,,0,0,0,,Drastic times call for drastic measures.
Dialogue: 10,0:03:46.05,0:03:47.59,GJM_Main,,0,0,0,,We're resuming our research.
Dialogue: 10,0:03:48.18,0:03:51.79,GJM_Main,,0,0,0,,Humanity will need weapons\Nto fight the Aragami.
Dialogue: 10,0:03:54.64,0:03:56.46,GJM_Main,,0,0,0,,You are all here today
Dialogue: 10,0:03:56.77,0:04:02.05,GJM_Main,,0,0,0,,for the installation of the guiding device\Nthat is the keystone of Operation Meteorite.
Dialogue: 10,0:04:02.82,0:04:06.39,GJM_Main,,0,0,0,,The work will be done by a special\Ntech team, but there will be risks.
Dialogue: 10,0:04:07.57,0:04:10.53,GJM_Main,,0,0,0,,Your mission is to protect them.
Dialogue: 10,0:04:11.74,0:04:16.73,GJM_Main,,0,0,0,,There are five devices,\Nso you will be divided into five units.
Dialogue: 10,0:04:17.12,0:04:20.37,GJM_Main,,0,0,0,,Those who will lead\Nthe units are as follows:
Dialogue: 10,0:04:21.63,0:04:22.49,GJM_Main,,0,0,0,,Tachibana Sakuya.
Dialogue: 10,0:04:23.54,0:04:24.99,GJM_Main,,0,0,0,,Oomori Tatsumi.
Dialogue: 10,0:04:25.46,0:04:27.21,GJM_Main,,0,0,0,,Brendan Bardell.
Dialogue: 10,0:04:27.21,0:04:29.09,GJM_Main,,0,0,0,,Gina Dickinson.
Dialogue: 10,0:04:29.09,0:04:30.38,GJM_Main,,0,0,0,,Utsugi Lenka.
Dialogue: 10,0:04:35.01,0:04:36.92,GJM_Main,,0,0,0,,Lenka... is in charge?
Dialogue: 10,0:04:36.92,0:04:38.09,GJM_Main,,0,0,0,,Wow!
Dialogue: 10,0:04:38.85,0:04:41.09,GJM_Main,,0,0,0,,I'm a unit leader?
Dialogue: 10,0:04:41.52,0:04:43.67,GJM_Main,,0,0,0,,But I don't have a God Arc...
Dialogue: 10,0:04:44.15,0:04:46.44,GJM_Main,,0,0,0,,I won't stop you if you choose to drop out.
Dialogue: 10,0:04:46.44,0:04:50.28,GJM_Main,,0,0,0,,This is a critical mission for Aegis.\NIs it too difficult for you?
Dialogue: 10,0:04:50.28,0:04:51.11,GJM_Main,,0,0,0,,Aegis...
Dialogue: 10,0:04:53.32,0:04:55.66,GJM_Main,,0,0,0,,No. My apologies.
Dialogue: 10,0:04:55.66,0:04:57.87,GJM_Main,,0,0,0,,I gladly accept.
Dialogue: 10,0:04:57.87,0:05:00.19,GJM_Main,,0,0,0,,Good. With that...
Dialogue: 10,0:05:00.19,0:05:02.96,GJM_Main,,0,0,0,,Soma, you'll be in Utsugi's unit.
Dialogue: 10,0:05:03.50,0:05:04.54,GJM_Main,,0,0,0,,Roger.
Dialogue: 10,0:05:06.84,0:05:08.76,GJM_Main,,0,0,0,,Soma... sir.
Dialogue: 10,0:05:09.97,0:05:11.30,GJM_Main,,0,0,0,,I'm honored.
Dialogue: 10,0:05:13.09,0:05:14.91,GJM_Main,,0,0,0,,Forget the formalities.
Dialogue: 10,0:05:17.81,0:05:19.85,GJM_Main,,0,0,0,,I feel sorry for you.
Dialogue: 10,0:05:21.52,0:05:24.92,GJM_Main,,0,0,0,,Watch your back around the Grim Reaper.
Dialogue: 10,0:05:25.86,0:05:27.32,GJM_Main,,0,0,0,,"Grim Reaper"?
Dialogue: 10,0:05:29.86,0:05:32.78,GJM_Main,,0,0,0,,Have you made your decision yet?
Dialogue: 10,0:05:32.78,0:05:34.32,GJM_Main,,0,0,0,,No, not yet...
Dialogue: 10,0:05:34.99,0:05:37.12,GJM_Main,,0,0,0,,I... just wanted to help...
Dialogue: 10,0:05:38.08,0:05:40.79,GJM_Main,,0,0,0,,If nothing else, it can serve as a shield.
Dialogue: 10,0:05:41.66,0:05:42.75,GJM_Main,,0,0,0,,That's fine.
Dialogue: 10,0:05:43.42,0:05:47.67,GJM_Main,,0,0,0,,As I explained earlier, using your God Arc\Nwill affect your life expectancy.
Dialogue: 10,0:05:48.25,0:05:51.34,GJM_Main,,0,0,0,,If you can't accept that, resign now.
Dialogue: 10,0:05:51.92,0:05:55.66,GJM_Main,,0,0,0,,If you're teamed up with Soma,\Nyou might not need to use it.
Dialogue: 10,0:05:56.35,0:05:58.81,GJM_Main,,0,0,0,,About Soma...
Dialogue: 10,0:06:01.31,0:06:03.05,GJM_Main,,0,0,0,,People keep calling him the "Grim Reaper".
Dialogue: 10,0:06:04.15,0:06:06.17,GJM_Main,,0,0,0,,"Grim Reaper"?
Dialogue: 10,0:06:06.69,0:06:08.48,GJM_Main,,0,0,0,,Fate is cruel.
Dialogue: 10,0:06:09.02,0:06:12.74,GJM_Main,,0,0,0,,It would be fair to say\Nthat both of you are victims of it.
Dialogue: 10,0:06:14.18,0:06:17.98,GJM_Main,,0,0,0,,If you want to know more,\Nlook him up in the database.
Dialogue: 10,0:06:18.62,0:06:20.87,GJM_Main,,0,0,0,,You can decide what\Nto think of him after that.
Dialogue: 10,0:06:25.15,0:06:27.59,GJM_Main,,0,0,0,,Soma...
Dialogue: 10,0:06:30.76,0:06:32.92,GJM_Main,,0,0,0,,Schicksal...
Dialogue: 10,0:06:47.98,0:06:48.86,GJM_Main,,0,0,0,,All right!
Dialogue: 10,0:06:53.86,0:06:55.74,GJM_Main,,0,0,0,,It was working on them before!
Dialogue: 10,0:06:56.36,0:06:58.02,GJM_Main,,0,0,0,,Retreat! Pull back!
Dialogue: 10,0:07:01.37,0:07:04.07,GJM_Main,,0,0,0,,The reports say it stopped working again.
Dialogue: 10,0:07:04.41,0:07:08.75,GJM_Main,,0,0,0,,No doubt the Aragami's\Nbias inclination has changed.
Dialogue: 10,0:07:08.75,0:07:11.32,GJM_Main,,0,0,0,,So the Aragami are evolving...
Dialogue: 10,0:07:11.80,0:07:14.88,GJM_Main,,0,0,0,,I told them it was too soon\Nfor practical application!
Dialogue: 10,0:07:14.88,0:07:17.05,GJM_Main,,0,0,0,,But we have proven that it works.
Dialogue: 10,0:07:17.05,0:07:19.39,GJM_Main,,0,0,0,,We've already saved so many.
Dialogue: 10,0:07:19.39,0:07:24.50,GJM_Main,,0,0,0,,But I'm worried about claiming\Nthat it'll solve all our problems.
Dialogue: 10,0:07:24.50,0:07:29.51,GJM_Main,,0,0,0,,Three more Eastern European nations\Nhave agreed to use Fenrir's technology.
Dialogue: 10,0:07:30.06,0:07:33.68,GJM_Main,,0,0,0,,This makes over 50 nations\Nto sign contracts with Fenrir.
Dialogue: 10,0:07:33.68,0:07:37.36,GJM_Main,,0,0,0,,There's a limit to what\Nexisting weaponry can do.
Dialogue: 10,0:07:37.95,0:07:40.95,GJM_Main,,0,0,0,,If we perfect the\NBias Factor in our weapons...
Dialogue: 10,0:07:41.53,0:07:46.50,GJM_Main,,0,0,0,,That Bias Factor will degrade the moment\Nit's extracted from the Oracle cells.
Dialogue: 10,0:07:47.33,0:07:49.21,GJM_Main,,0,0,0,,Take a look at this.
Dialogue: 10,0:07:50.84,0:07:52.03,GJM_Main,,0,0,0,,This is...
Dialogue: 10,0:07:52.55,0:07:54.42,GJM_Main,,0,0,0,,Did you design this?
Dialogue: 10,0:07:54.42,0:07:55.67,GJM_Main,,0,0,0,,Yes.
Dialogue: 10,0:07:55.67,0:08:00.43,GJM_Main,,0,0,0,,It's the only way a refined\NBias Factor will work in weapons.
Dialogue: 10,0:08:00.43,0:08:03.35,GJM_Main,,0,0,0,,But this isn't a conventional weapon...
Dialogue: 10,0:08:03.35,0:08:05.22,GJM_Main,,0,0,0,,It's a living weapon.
Dialogue: 10,0:08:05.22,0:08:08.42,GJM_Main,,0,0,0,,A morbid yet brilliant idea.
Dialogue: 10,0:08:08.94,0:08:14.01,GJM_Main,,0,0,0,,We can cultivate Oracle cells ourselves\Nto create artificial Aragami.
Dialogue: 10,0:08:14.36,0:08:16.49,GJM_Main,,0,0,0,,However, there's one problem.
Dialogue: 10,0:08:17.82,0:08:23.58,GJM_Main,,0,0,0,,If it's made up of Oracle cells,\Nit'll devour anything it touches.
Dialogue: 10,0:08:23.58,0:08:25.54,GJM_Main,,0,0,0,,Can't it be controlled remotely?
Dialogue: 10,0:08:26.08,0:08:29.11,GJM_Main,,0,0,0,,It's a living being and as such,\Nwould be hard to control.
Dialogue: 10,0:08:29.46,0:08:32.42,GJM_Main,,0,0,0,,Analyzing it would be a long process.
Dialogue: 10,0:08:34.30,0:08:36.87,GJM_Main,,0,0,0,,There is one possibility...
Dialogue: 10,0:08:39.30,0:08:45.37,GJM_Main,,0,0,0,,We could inject the Bias Factor into\Na human and let their body adapt to it.
Dialogue: 10,0:08:47.00,0:08:48.35,GJM_Main,,0,0,0,,That's...
Dialogue: 10,0:08:48.85,0:08:52.51,GJM_Main,,0,0,0,,Indeed, that would be\Nthe most effective method.
Dialogue: 10,0:08:53.27,0:08:56.01,GJM_Main,,0,0,0,,But to do something so hellish...{ep8 preview line}
Dialogue: 10,0:08:56.32,0:08:59.70,GJM_Main,,0,0,0,,We'd need an incredible amount\Nof volunteers to test it.
Dialogue: 10,0:08:59.70,0:09:06.62,GJM_Main,,0,0,0,,Administering it via the womb could\Nmake adaptation far safer than a direct dosage.
Dialogue: 10,0:09:06.62,0:09:11.25,GJM_Main,,0,0,0,,Maybe so, but who would\Npossibly agree to it?!
Dialogue: 10,0:09:11.25,0:09:12.74,GJM_Main,,0,0,0,,I will.
Dialogue: 10,0:09:13.25,0:09:14.20,GJM_Main,,0,0,0,,What?
Dialogue: 10,0:09:15.04,0:09:18.76,GJM_Main,,0,0,0,,Or should I say that {\i1}we{\i0} will.
Dialogue: 10,0:09:34.73,0:09:38.30,GJM_Main,,0,0,0,,I hear you're going on the mission\Nwith the New-Type.
Dialogue: 10,0:09:39.57,0:09:42.45,GJM_Main,,0,0,0,,It's an important device, so don't break it.
Dialogue: 10,0:09:51.71,0:09:52.58,GJM_Main,,0,0,0,,Hey.
Dialogue: 10,0:09:53.92,0:09:55.25,GJM_Main,,0,0,0,,Rindou.
Dialogue: 10,0:09:55.25,0:09:58.25,GJM_Main,,0,0,0,,Quit staring off into space.\NI've been looking for you.
Dialogue: 10,0:09:58.75,0:10:01.33,GJM_Main,,0,0,0,,I just wanted a change of scenery.
Dialogue: 10,0:10:02.13,0:10:06.43,GJM_Main,,0,0,0,,I haven't seen you around either.\NWhere have you been?
Dialogue: 10,0:10:06.43,0:10:07.30,GJM_Main,,0,0,0,,Huh?
Dialogue: 10,0:10:07.30,0:10:10.31,GJM_Main,,0,0,0,,Oh, you know, I was on a date.\NNothing special.
Dialogue: 10,0:10:10.89,0:10:12.23,GJM_Main,,0,0,0,,A ladies' man, huh?
Dialogue: 10,0:10:18.44,0:10:21.01,GJM_Main,,0,0,0,,You and Soma have a mission?
Dialogue: 10,0:10:21.69,0:10:25.32,GJM_Main,,0,0,0,,If left to his own devices,\Nhe'd go out there to die.
Dialogue: 10,0:10:25.32,0:10:27.20,GJM_Main,,0,0,0,,Keep your eyes on him.
Dialogue: 10,0:10:27.20,0:10:29.02,GJM_Main,,0,0,0,,That's all I wanted to say.
Dialogue: 10,0:10:43.78,0:10:47.79,GJM_Main,,0,0,0,,So we need to place these stakes\Naround the guiding device?
Dialogue: 10,0:10:47.79,0:10:48.79,GJM_Main,,0,0,0,,Yes.
Dialogue: 10,0:10:49.29,0:10:52.92,GJM_Main,,0,0,0,,Once activated,\Na mock defense wall will be formed.
Dialogue: 10,0:10:52.92,0:10:57.55,GJM_Main,,0,0,0,,And until the operation starts,\Nthe devices will be safe from the Aragami.
Dialogue: 10,0:10:58.17,0:11:00.76,GJM_Main,,0,0,0,,This technology is still being refined, however.
Dialogue: 10,0:11:00.76,0:11:04.60,GJM_Main,,0,0,0,,We won't know how durable it is until it's tested.
Dialogue: 10,0:11:06.18,0:11:06.97,GJM_Main,,0,0,0,,Come in.
Dialogue: 10,0:11:07.47,0:11:11.48,GJM_Main,,0,0,0,,Major Amamiya, the new recruits\Nwill begin training at 1200 hours.
Dialogue: 10,0:11:11.48,0:11:13.48,GJM_Main,,0,0,0,,Understood. I'll be there shortly.
Dialogue: 10,0:11:15.40,0:11:17.57,GJM_Main,,0,0,0,,That's it for explanations.
Dialogue: 10,0:11:17.57,0:11:21.74,GJM_Main,,0,0,0,,The guiding devices are vital.\NYou know what to do, Utsugi.
Dialogue: 10,0:11:21.74,0:11:23.95,GJM_Main,,0,0,0,,Um... Major Amamiya.
Dialogue: 10,0:11:25.45,0:11:29.12,GJM_Main,,0,0,0,,Why did you step down as a God Eater?
Dialogue: 10,0:11:30.91,0:11:34.75,GJM_Main,,0,0,0,,Have you ever seen an Aragami being born?
Dialogue: 10,0:11:36.25,0:11:37.13,GJM_Main,,0,0,0,,No.
Dialogue: 10,0:11:37.63,0:11:39.38,GJM_Main,,0,0,0,,If you did, you'd think the same...
Dialogue: 10,0:11:40.59,0:11:44.39,GJM_Main,,0,0,0,,That Aragami cannot be exterminated.
Dialogue: 10,0:11:45.39,0:11:46.76,GJM_Main,,0,0,0,,No way!
Dialogue: 10,0:11:46.76,0:11:47.60,GJM_Main,,0,0,0,,However...
Dialogue: 10,0:11:48.81,0:11:52.65,GJM_Main,,0,0,0,,I have faith that some day this will all end.
Dialogue: 10,0:11:53.23,0:11:58.73,GJM_Main,,0,0,0,,So I chose to nurture the next generation\Nand entrust the future to them.
Dialogue: 10,0:11:59.32,0:12:00.15,GJM_Main,,0,0,0,,The future...
Dialogue: 10,0:12:00.65,0:12:02.91,GJM_Main,,0,0,0,,You'll understand in time.
Dialogue: 10,0:12:11.66,0:12:14.08,GJM_Main,,0,0,0,,I'm told the guiding devices are invaluable.
Dialogue: 10,0:12:14.67,0:12:17.75,GJM_Main,,0,0,0,,If we fail, the completion of Aegis will be delayed.
Dialogue: 10,0:12:18.50,0:12:20.88,GJM_Main,,0,0,0,,Let's work together to make this a success.
Dialogue: 10,0:12:21.76,0:12:23.34,GJM_Main,,0,0,0,,Any questions?
Dialogue: 10,0:12:23.76,0:12:26.14,GJM_Main,,0,0,0,,Not really, but...
Dialogue: 10,0:12:26.72,0:12:28.10,GJM_Main,,0,0,0,,I'm a little nervous.
Dialogue: 10,0:12:28.68,0:12:32.60,GJM_Main,,0,0,0,,People who go out with Soma...\Ndon't come back.
Dialogue: 10,0:12:34.02,0:12:35.52,GJM_Main,,0,0,0,,It's just a rumor, but—
Dialogue: 10,0:12:35.52,0:12:36.15,GJM_Main,,0,0,0,,Hey.
Dialogue: 10,0:12:37.27,0:12:40.57,GJM_Main,,0,0,0,,If you don't want to die,\Nthen stay away from me.
Dialogue: 10,0:12:41.15,0:12:42.36,GJM_Main,,0,0,0,,You too.
Dialogue: 10,0:12:45.86,0:12:49.28,GJM_Main,,0,0,0,,If worse comes to worst,\Nforget the device and run.
Dialogue: 10,0:13:05.22,0:13:08.01,GJM_Main,,0,0,0,,The guiding devices have been set up.
Dialogue: 10,0:13:08.01,0:13:08.85,GJM_Main,,0,0,0,,Good work.
Dialogue: 10,0:13:09.97,0:13:11.14,GJM_Main,,0,0,0,,Soma, sir!
Dialogue: 10,0:13:32.41,0:13:33.33,GJM_Main,,0,0,0,,Incredible...
Dialogue: 10,0:13:33.33,0:13:34.96,GJM_Main,,0,0,0,,Don't just stand there.
Dialogue: 10,0:13:35.29,0:13:37.00,GJM_Main,,0,0,0,,Get on with it.
Dialogue: 10,0:13:37.00,0:13:38.71,GJM_Main,,0,0,0,,R-Right.
Dialogue: 10,0:13:46.93,0:13:47.72,GJM_Main,,0,0,0,,All right.
Dialogue: 10,0:13:48.76,0:13:51.43,GJM_Main,,0,0,0,,Objective complete. Let's head back.
Dialogue: 10,0:13:51.43,0:13:52.14,GJM_Main,,0,0,0,,Wait.
Dialogue: 10,0:13:56.77,0:13:57.60,GJM_Main,,0,0,0,,What is that?
Dialogue: 10,0:14:02.36,0:14:03.19,GJM_Main,,0,0,0,,An Aragami?!
Dialogue: 10,0:14:04.48,0:14:08.11,GJM_Main,,0,0,0,,{\i1\t(3158,0,\3c&HFFFFFF&\4c&HFFFFFF&)}Have you ever seen an Aragami being born?
Dialogue: 10,0:14:14.08,0:14:15.58,GJM_Main,,0,0,0,,They came right out of the ground...
Dialogue: 10,0:14:15.58,0:14:17.83,GJM_Main,,0,0,0,,{\i1}Aragami cannot be exterminated.
Dialogue: 10,0:14:19.79,0:14:20.67,GJM_Main,,0,0,0,,Look.
Dialogue: 10,0:14:26.80,0:14:27.93,GJM_Main,,0,0,0,,It's working!
Dialogue: 10,0:14:35.47,0:14:36.48,GJM_Main,,0,0,0,,The wall!
Dialogue: 10,0:14:40.35,0:14:42.56,GJM_Main,,0,0,0,,This is bad! What do we do?
Dialogue: 10,0:14:46.11,0:14:47.15,GJM_Main,,0,0,0,,Damn it!
Dialogue: 10,0:14:48.57,0:14:49.91,GJM_Main,,0,0,0,,Soma, sir!
Dialogue: 10,0:14:58.66,0:14:59.96,GJM_Main,,0,0,0,,Come at me.
Dialogue: 10,0:15:00.83,0:15:02.71,GJM_Main,,0,0,0,,Is he going to protect the guiding device?!
Dialogue: 10,0:15:03.46,0:15:04.88,GJM_Main,,0,0,0,,Bring the copter down!
Dialogue: 10,0:15:04.88,0:15:06.21,GJM_Main,,0,0,0,,What are you doing?!
Dialogue: 10,0:15:06.21,0:15:08.05,GJM_Main,,0,0,0,,Retrieving the guiding device!
Dialogue: 10,0:15:08.05,0:15:09.42,GJM_Main,,0,0,0,,You've gotta be kidding!
Dialogue: 10,0:15:10.09,0:15:14.85,GJM_Main,,0,0,0,,It's over for us if the wall is destroyed\Nwhile we try to salvage the device!
Dialogue: 10,0:15:14.85,0:15:17.56,GJM_Main,,0,0,0,,Are you even able to\Nprotect us with your God Arc?
Dialogue: 10,0:15:18.43,0:15:19.27,GJM_Main,,0,0,0,,That's...
Dialogue: 10,0:15:19.27,0:15:20.73,GJM_Main,,0,0,0,,You guys stay on board.
Dialogue: 10,0:15:21.85,0:15:23.23,GJM_Main,,0,0,0,,You'll only be in the way.
Dialogue: 10,0:15:38.62,0:15:42.17,GJM_Main,,0,0,0,,Leave the device!\NYou can't take all of them on!
Dialogue: 10,0:15:43.13,0:15:44.33,GJM_Main,,0,0,0,,Soma, sir!
Dialogue: 10,0:15:44.33,0:15:45.84,GJM_Main,,0,0,0,,{\i1}A monster.{ep8 preview line}
Dialogue: 10,0:15:45.84,0:15:48.26,GJM_Main,,0,0,0,,{\i1}All of his partners die...
Dialogue: 10,0:15:48.26,0:15:49.59,GJM_Main,,0,0,0,,{\i1}A Grim Reaper.
Dialogue: 10,0:15:50.22,0:15:53.39,GJM_Main,,0,0,0,,{\i1}An unholy child who killed\Nhis mother to be born.{ep8 preview line}
Dialogue: 10,0:15:54.26,0:15:56.26,GJM_Main,,0,0,0,,If anyone dies, it'll be me.{ep8 preview line}
Dialogue: 10,0:16:00.60,0:16:01.77,GJM_Main,,0,0,0,,{\i1}Don't tell me...
Dialogue: 10,0:16:02.73,0:16:03.90,GJM_Main,,0,0,0,,{\i1}you're pregnant?!
Dialogue: 10,0:16:04.56,0:16:06.69,GJM_Main,,0,0,0,,A-Are you serious?
Dialogue: 10,0:16:06.69,0:16:08.98,GJM_Main,,0,0,0,,Congratulations, Johannes!
Dialogue: 10,0:16:09.78,0:16:12.28,GJM_Main,,0,0,0,,Oh, but...
Dialogue: 10,0:16:12.82,0:16:14.66,GJM_Main,,0,0,0,,Considering the situation...
Dialogue: 10,0:16:14.66,0:16:19.16,GJM_Main,,0,0,0,,Paylor's idea is the best possible choice.
Dialogue: 10,0:16:19.87,0:16:23.29,GJM_Main,,0,0,0,,As a fellow researcher,\NI would be the ideal candidate.
Dialogue: 10,0:16:23.71,0:16:26.88,GJM_Main,,0,0,0,,But if this should fail...
Dialogue: 10,0:16:26.88,0:16:30.17,GJM_Main,,0,0,0,,You... and our baby...
Dialogue: 10,0:16:31.55,0:16:33.59,GJM_Main,,0,0,0,,There's got to be another way!
Dialogue: 10,0:16:33.59,0:16:35.43,GJM_Main,,0,0,0,,Let's keep thinking!
Dialogue: 10,0:16:35.43,0:16:37.18,GJM_Main,,0,0,0,,I agree with him.
Dialogue: 10,0:16:37.18,0:16:39.93,GJM_Main,,0,0,0,,Besides, we don't have to decide now.
Dialogue: 10,0:16:40.52,0:16:45.44,GJM_Main,,0,0,0,,There's no time left for mankind...
Dialogue: 10,0:16:46.19,0:16:49.94,GJM_Main,,0,0,0,,Don't worry about me, Johannes, Paylor.
Dialogue: 10,0:16:50.82,0:16:52.03,GJM_Main,,0,0,0,,I want...
Dialogue: 10,0:16:53.15,0:16:56.41,GJM_Main,,0,0,0,,to give hope to my baby\Nand to the future humanity.
Dialogue: 10,0:16:58.07,0:16:59.03,GJM_Main,,0,0,0,,No way.
Dialogue: 10,0:17:00.37,0:17:02.33,GJM_Main,,0,0,0,,Position the copter above the device!
Dialogue: 10,0:17:19.55,0:17:20.43,GJM_Main,,0,0,0,,Utsugi?
Dialogue: 10,0:17:23.81,0:17:26.23,GJM_Main,,0,0,0,,What are you doing?! Disconnect the device!
Dialogue: 10,0:17:26.23,0:17:30.15,GJM_Main,,0,0,0,,Soma, attack like you did\Nbefore and kill them all!
Dialogue: 10,0:17:36.53,0:17:38.62,GJM_Main,,0,0,0,,There's no time to reposition...
Dialogue: 10,0:17:39.12,0:17:40.08,GJM_Main,,0,0,0,,Shoot!
Dialogue: 10,0:17:45.08,0:17:48.54,GJM_Main,,0,0,0,,You didn't kill your mother to be born!
Dialogue: 10,0:17:50.09,0:17:51.04,GJM_Main,,0,0,0,,You...
Dialogue: 10,0:17:51.84,0:17:56.84,GJM_Main,,0,0,0,,You were entrusted with hope.\NHope that your mother passed on to you.
Dialogue: 10,0:17:57.13,0:17:59.85,GJM_Main,,0,0,0,,I don't see the Grim Reaper in you, so shoot!{ep8 preview line}
Dialogue: 10,0:18:00.30,0:18:01.76,GJM_Main,,0,0,0,,Soma!
Dialogue: 10,0:18:01.76,0:18:02.81,GJM_Main,,0,0,0,,Damn it!
Dialogue: 10,0:18:23.37,0:18:24.54,GJM_Main,,0,0,0,,Damn!
Dialogue: 10,0:18:25.33,0:18:26.25,GJM_Main,,0,0,0,,I told you.
Dialogue: 10,0:18:30.38,0:18:32.50,GJM_Main,,0,0,0,,You're not a Grim Reaper.
Dialogue: 10,0:18:33.55,0:18:34.76,GJM_Main,,0,0,0,,Utsugi...
Dialogue: 10,0:18:37.97,0:18:40.09,GJM_Main,,0,0,0,,Hey! Utsugi!
Dialogue: 10,0:18:47.64,0:18:48.94,GJM_Main,,0,0,0,,You're awake.
Dialogue: 10,0:18:51.23,0:18:53.19,GJM_Main,,0,0,0,,What happened to the device?
Dialogue: 10,0:18:53.19,0:18:54.61,GJM_Main,,0,0,0,,It's fine.
Dialogue: 10,0:18:55.90,0:18:58.28,GJM_Main,,0,0,0,,You looked me up in the database, didn't you?
Dialogue: 10,0:18:59.49,0:19:01.95,GJM_Main,,0,0,0,,You think you know what kind of person I am?
Dialogue: 10,0:19:04.95,0:19:09.71,GJM_Main,,0,0,0,,Maybe not, but I think I understand a little now.
Dialogue: 10,0:19:10.62,0:19:14.63,GJM_Main,,0,0,0,,Because I have people who make life worth living.
Dialogue: 10,0:19:16.50,0:19:19.72,GJM_Main,,0,0,0,,Why'd you accept the mission in your condition?
Dialogue: 10,0:19:20.51,0:19:22.51,GJM_Main,,0,0,0,,In order to complete Aegis.
Dialogue: 10,0:19:23.14,0:19:25.81,GJM_Main,,0,0,0,,What good is completing something like that?
Dialogue: 10,0:19:27.31,0:19:30.69,GJM_Main,,0,0,0,,You can't destroy Aragami\Nunless you destroy their cores.
Dialogue: 10,0:19:31.19,0:19:33.52,GJM_Main,,0,0,0,,And even if you destroy their cores,
Dialogue: 10,0:19:33.52,0:19:39.49,GJM_Main,,0,0,0,,the scattered Oracle cells will amass again\Nand give birth to more Aragami.
Dialogue: 10,0:19:39.49,0:19:42.49,GJM_Main,,0,0,0,,It's a cycle of despair.{ep8 preview line}
Dialogue: 10,0:19:43.99,0:19:46.83,GJM_Main,,0,0,0,,Then pass it on to someone.
Dialogue: 10,0:19:47.83,0:19:50.25,GJM_Main,,0,0,0,,The same way your mother did.
Dialogue: 10,0:19:51.04,0:19:55.54,GJM_Main,,0,0,0,,You can't die until you connect\Nyour life to someone else's.
Dialogue: 10,0:20:05.80,0:20:08.27,GJM_Main,,0,0,0,,I didn't die,
Dialogue: 10,0:20:09.10,0:20:10.56,GJM_Main,,0,0,0,,so you don't get to die either.
Dialogue: 10,0:20:19.53,0:20:20.61,GJM_Main,,0,0,0,,Soma?
Dialogue: 10,0:20:21.28,0:20:22.86,GJM_Main,,0,0,0,,Like the Indian legend?
Dialogue: 10,0:20:23.70,0:20:26.49,GJM_Main,,0,0,0,,Yes. Do you not like it?
Dialogue: 10,0:20:26.49,0:20:31.91,GJM_Main,,0,0,0,,A nectar of the gods that bestows\Nthe force of life to mankind...
Dialogue: 10,0:20:32.54,0:20:37.38,GJM_Main,,0,0,0,,I believe that it's something humanity needs now.
Dialogue: 10,0:20:38.04,0:20:39.05,GJM_Main,,0,0,0,,You're right...
Dialogue: 10,0:20:39.75,0:20:41.21,GJM_Main,,0,0,0,,It's a fine name.
Dialogue: 10,0:20:41.55,0:20:42.63,GJM_Main,,0,0,0,,I'm glad.
Dialogue: 10,0:20:43.26,0:20:47.05,GJM_Main,,0,0,0,,We can't wait to see you, Soma.
Dialogue: 10,0:20:55.52,0:20:56.56,GJM_Main,,0,0,0,,A dam?
Dialogue: 10,0:20:57.11,0:21:02.57,GJM_Main,,0,0,0,,Yes... It was surrounded by a forest\Nand there were people...
Dialogue: 10,0:21:03.36,0:21:08.58,GJM_Main,,0,0,0,,Amamiya Rindou seems to have\Nsome association with these people.
Dialogue: 10,0:21:09.20,0:21:10.08,GJM_Main,,0,0,0,,Yes.
Dialogue: 10,0:21:10.91,0:21:14.58,GJM_Main,,0,0,0,,Everyone seemed quite close.
Dialogue: 10,0:21:18.08,0:21:20.75,GJM_Main,,0,0,0,,You didn't heed my warning.
Dialogue: 10,0:21:21.17,0:21:22.21,GJM_Main,,0,0,0,,I'm sorry.
Dialogue: 10,0:21:23.13,0:21:25.05,GJM_Main,,0,0,0,,And you understand what that means?
Dialogue: 10,0:21:26.05,0:21:26.68,GJM_Main,,0,0,0,,Yes.
Dialogue: 10,0:21:27.30,0:21:29.55,GJM_Main,,0,0,0,,I see. Then you'll retire—
Dialogue: 10,0:21:29.55,0:21:30.68,GJM_Main,,0,0,0,,Please fix it.
Dialogue: 10,0:21:32.89,0:21:34.68,GJM_Main,,0,0,0,,Please fix my God Arc.
Dialogue: 10,0:21:35.02,0:21:36.27,GJM_Main,,0,0,0,,What did you say?
Dialogue: 10,0:21:36.94,0:21:38.90,GJM_Main,,0,0,0,,One more thing.
Dialogue: 10,0:21:38.90,0:21:42.19,GJM_Main,,0,0,0,,Please don't tell anyone about my condition.
Dialogue: 10,0:21:46.40,0:21:49.24,GJM_Main,,0,0,0,,You certainly are fascinating, boy.
Dialogue: 10,0:21:49.24,0:21:52.29,GJM_Main,,0,0,0,,Very well then. I'll restore your God Arc.
Dialogue: 10,0:21:53.62,0:21:55.62,GJM_Main,,0,0,0,,But let me ask you one thing.
Dialogue: 10,0:21:57.17,0:21:57.96,GJM_Main,,0,0,0,,Why?
Dialogue: 10,0:22:07.68,0:22:10.64,GJM_Main,,0,0,0,,Is this the thing that's calling out to them?
Dialogue: 10,0:22:11.51,0:22:16.52,GJM_Main,,0,0,0,,This is the Aragami that devoured\Nyour mother and father.
Dialogue: 10,0:22:17.02,0:22:19.73,GJM_Main,,0,0,0,,Mother... Father...
Dialogue: 10,0:22:20.27,0:22:24.44,GJM_Main,,0,0,0,,But don't worry. You can fight now.
Dialogue: 10,0:22:25.24,0:22:29.36,GJM_Main,,0,0,0,,Tell me what I taught you.\NYou can pull the trigger.
Dialogue: 10,0:22:30.28,0:22:33.54,GJM_Main,,0,0,0,,You... taught me...
Dialogue: 10,0:22:35.08,0:22:35.62,GJM_Main,,0,0,0,,One...
Dialogue: 10,0:22:37.21,0:22:38.21,GJM_Main,,0,0,0,,Two...
Dialogue: 10,0:22:41.33,0:22:42.46,GJM_Main,,0,0,0,,Three...
Dialogue: 10,0:22:43.34,0:22:45.05,GJM_Main,,0,0,0,,Good job.
Dialogue: 10,0:22:45.71,0:22:47.47,GJM_Main,,0,0,0,,This is your enemy.
Dialogue: 10,0:22:48.55,0:22:49.93,GJM_Main,,0,0,0,,An Aragami.
Dialogue: 10,0:22:55.43,0:22:56.68,GJM_Main,,0,0,0,,Doctor...
Dialogue: 10,0:22:56.68,0:23:00.15,GJM_Main,,0,0,0,,Are you saying that... this is a God Arc?!
Dialogue: 10,0:23:00.81,0:23:04.65,GJM_Main,,0,0,0,,I designed this with his compatibility rate in mind.
Dialogue: 10,0:23:07.78,0:23:09.15,GJM_Main,,0,0,0,,Aisha...
Dialogue: 10,0:23:09.82,0:23:13.16,GJM_Main,,0,0,0,,The hope for the future which you entrusted...
Dialogue: 10,0:23:14.12,0:23:17.16,GJM_Main,,0,0,0,,I won't let anyone get in the way of it.
Comment: 10,0:23:25.03,0:23:25.07,GJM_Main,,0,0,0,,{preview}
Dialogue: 10,0:23:26.21,0:23:29.01,GJM_Main,,0,0,0,,{\q2}Can I become strong enough to take down Aragami?!{ep10, 08:54}
Dialogue: 10,0:23:29.01,0:23:30.55,GJM_Main,,0,0,0,,I'm Utsugi Iroha, his older sister.{ep10, 09:43}
Dialogue: 10,0:23:30.18,0:23:32.68,GJM_Overlap,,0,0,0,,{\an8}It'll always lead you in the right direction.{ep10, 09:59}
Dialogue: 10,0:23:31.80,0:23:34.55,GJM_Main,,0,0,0,,Sometimes you have to choose.{ep10, 11:20}
Dialogue: 10,0:23:34.55,0:23:35.60,GJM_Main,,0,0,0,,...take care of Lenka.{ep10, 17:46}
Dialogue: 10,0:23:35.60,0:23:37.77,GJM_Main,,0,0,0,,You're such a hopeless brother.{ep10, 20:02}
Dialogue: 10,0:23:37.77,0:23:39.43,GJM_Main,,0,0,0,,...tell us your purpose.{ep10, 22:47}
